name: Ishi Go
description: $ISHI is a tribute to the true origin of the Shiba Inu breed. Ishi, born in 1930, is recognized as the official Father of the Shiba Inu. This project honors the legacy and history behind one of the most iconic dog lineages in the world, which later inspired legendary tokens like $DOGE, $SHIB, $FLOKI, $CHEEMS, $BONK, and $NEIRO. $ISHI brings this story on-chain for a new generation of holders to celebrate and preserve.
